entries.femaleVariant: Any thoughts?
Any idea how we could do that?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Ay, huele feo" b="" a=", this meat. Ack... I can taste it..."/>
Armored shutter – there's no way we're gettin' through that.
Old-ass factory, though. Bound to be tech tunnels and shafts and shit all over the place.
It's a production line. Plus, I thought you loved meat.
Buh... really no other way?
Can't hurt to try.
Unload on 'em, V! Cut loose!
Mmm... We gotta find a way outta here.
Now let's get outta here. I'm dyin' for some fresh air.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="¡Muerte, cabrón!" t="Die, fucker!" b="" a=""/>
Fire up the belt already, V. Ugh...
Oof, good. It's movin', let's go.
Then let's go. Quicker the better.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Vámonos." t="Let's go already." b="" a=""/>
<mothertongue l="mex" m="¡Mierda!" b="" a=" We're cut off."/>
Virus must've tripped a security protocol.
Fuck! They just killed Royce!
Grab the gear – bot and control shard. Quick!
Got the set – bot and controller.
